latestIgtvVideos.title: Kama Auyrveda  VS  Shesha Beauty
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@sheshaayurveda Pure Rose Water
@kamaayurveda Pure Rose Water
  So I choose to improvise as much as I can and here I am with yet another video. Hope you all love it .
 Some things I would like to mention here that I took this video at my mum's place at terrace in bright sunlight as I don't own a ring light as of now .So you will see some transitions in brightness. 
  Secondly ,all my nephews are standing right in front of me wandering what is happening 😄😄.
 Ok too much, I would like to mention one thing that I saw in @anusha.gorthy stories that Shesha beauty Rose water is made in small batches so you get the freshest rose water whereas the Kama one is made in huge quantities .
Keep on the comments coming if you have more points of comparison. Let everyone know...❣❣❣
#sheshanaturals #sheshabeauty #sheshaayurveda
